# Standing order — Use the CQRS Wizard before CQRS-shaped edits

`decision_key`: `architecture-policy::agent-behavior::cqrs-wizard-before-cqrs-edits`

Before editing CQRS operation models, handlers, MCP wrappers, or operation catalog registration paths, run praxis_operation_forge for operation path inspection and praxis_evolve_operation_field for existing input-shape changes. Manual edits are allowed only after the Wizard says the operation already exists or returns the file-by-file evolution plan. Search terms: CQRS Wizard, operation forge, evolve operation field, operation_catalog_registry, input_model_ref, handler_ref.

